# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Tauri updater signing keys — NEVER commit private keys
# Canonical local path: ~/.tauri/remedy.key  (and .pub)
# Public key is embedded in desktop/src-tauri/tauri.conf.json (safe to commit)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.tauri/
**/.tauri/
*.key
*.key.pub
remedy.key
remedy.key.pub
**/remedy.key
**/remedy.key.pub
# Local update signatures (regenerated by CI / tauri signer)
*.sig
*.exe.sig
